{
  "stem": "12255.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not in the rooms, of course, but-- but at least it was a tremendous advance on the horror camp in which they had been living, where one on top of the other were-- were defecating and everything else.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hardly-- hardly any facilities, and the sick were lying there dying, and everything was mixed up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we transferred these people slowly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a very interesting facet was that the great majority were women.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somehow or other, they had been able to withstand more than the men.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the majority were women, and many of these-- most of them-- had formed little groups with older women and younger women, and even young-- youngsters, teenagers, and-- and formed little families.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when we were trying to move them, we had to try and move the little families together.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if you had a room which was allocated for five, and the family was six, then you had a bit of a problem.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was at this stage-- if I may interpolate-- it was at this stage that I met a man who became a great figure in the world of the displaced persons, named [?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yossele ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Rosensaft. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yossele ?] was a little man, Polish Jew, a former, obviously, union organizer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he began to help in the organization, not through us, but on his own.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and while I was trying to fit-- I'll never forget-- while I was trying to fit some people into a particular room, he came along and tried to undo what I was doing, and I got hold of him by the scruff of his neck, and told him to get away.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And mind you, he never held it against me, because we became quite friendly afterwards.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
